   <concept id="DFARS_218.204" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.2">
      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">218.204</ph> Humanitarian or peacekeepingoperation.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p>The following requirements do not apply to acquisitions
that, as determined by the head of the contracting activity, are
in support of humanitarian or peacekeeping operations:</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(1) <i>Policy for item unique identification
at <xref href="211.274-2.dita#DFARS_211.274-2" base="DFARS-211.274-2" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">211.274-2</xref>(a).</i> See <xref href="211.274-2.dita#DFARS_211.274-2" base="DFARS-211.274-2" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">211.274-2</xref>(b).</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(2) <i>Only one offer requirements at sections</i>
            <xref href="215.371-2.dita#DFARS_215.371-2" base="DFARS-215.371-2" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">215.371-2</xref>. See <xref href="215.371-4.dita#DFARS_215.371-4" base="DFARS-215.371-4" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">215.371-4</xref>(a)(2).</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(3) <i>Approval of determination and findings
for time-and-materials or labor-hour contracts at <xref href="216.601.dita#DFARS_216.601" base="DFARS-216.601" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">216.601</xref>(d)(i)(A)(1) and
(2).</i> See <xref href="216.601.dita#DFARS_216.601" base="DFARS-216.601" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">216.601</xref>(d)(3).</p>
      </conbody>
